So far we have demonstrated that keybord,mouse and Xbox Gamepad can get parameters. 

You can create a Application for get devices parameter.

Step1 Create a new Unity project.

Step2 Setting 28 Input parameters,only "Axis" will change.[ProjectSetting=>Input] 
(reference https://github.com/RAYU2017/Unity_ShowKeycodeAndJoysticks/blob/main/Input%E5%8F%83%E6%95%B8%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A.PNG)

Step3 Create "Canvas" and create 29 "Text"s in subtyping ,final add this "Script".
(reference https://github.com/RAYU2017/Unity_ShowKeycodeAndJoysticks/blob/main/ShowKeycodeAndJoysticks.cs)

*Introduction about Xbox gamepad buttons.
(reference https://github.com/RAYU2017/Unity_ShowKeycodeAndJoysticks/blob/main/Xbox%20gamepad%20buttons.png)

